  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Modern Irrigation and Land\nCo, are laying out a large tract of\nland in ten acre tracts six miles east\nof Howard street, in the garden\nspot of the Spokane valley which\nthey propose to irrigate from wells,\noperated by electricity. This tract\nis the cream of the Spokane valley.\nThe company is DESTROYS of an appro-\npirate name and will pay 500 for the\nname they adopt. Competition open\nto all. All names must be In by\nJanuary 20. Address Modern Irriga-\nton Gland Co., Wolverton Block,\nSpokane, Wash.\n\n\nSt. Paul"
    }
